==Trivia==
*Her name is a pun on the phrase "fair enough".
*Fairy Nuff's dialogue during Fairytale Part I has a line where she says that she put the Fairy Queen to sleep after the Queen's battle with [[Tanglefoot]]. She says she put the Queen in a state of "tempus fugit" which is a Latin phrase, "time flies." She says this state will slow time down for the Queen so that she may stay alive longer.
*She once saved Zandar from an apparently mortal injury he sustained whilst studying [[otherworldly being]]s.

